section.section:
Lease payments to the Authority appropriated by the State shall be transferred to:
the Baltimore Convention Fund if appropriated for a Baltimore Convention facility;
the Camden Yards Fund if appropriated for a sports facility or other facility at Camden Yards;
the Hippodrome Performing Arts Fund if appropriated for a Hippodrome Performing Arts facility;
the Montgomery County Conference Fund if appropriated for a Montgomery County Conference facility; or
the Ocean City Convention Fund if appropriated for an Ocean City Convention facility.

text.section:
The Authority shall:
in cooperation with Baltimore City, appoint a task force that includes residents and business and institutional representatives from the area adjacent to Camden Yards to review the schematic, preliminary, and final plans for facilities at Camden Yards;
submit schematic plans for development of Camden Yards and the Baltimore Convention site to Baltimore City for review and comment before acquiring any property;
submit preliminary and final plans for Baltimore facilities to Baltimore City for review and comment; and
participate in the design review processes of Baltimore City.
